￼# NKLinearProgressView

#ProgressView that shows the progress percentile.

#How to use
#Take a UIView and set the class as NKLinearProgressView
#You can modify the appearance by setting the properties through the storyboard or by making an outlet for the view.
@IBOutlet weak var progressView : NKLinearProgressView!
progressView.barColor = UIColor.green
progressView.trackColor = UIColor.yellow
progressView.barThickness = 10
progressView.barPadding = 0
progressView.trackPadding = 6
progressView.progressValue = 50
#Using Storyboard #Just set the values from property inspector ￼
